description:
Mysteryville 2

Return to the eye-popping fun of Mysteryville in this 
sequel to one of our most popular games. After solving 
the cat caper of Mysteryville it&#039;s time for Laura, 
ace reporter, to get some well deserved rest.
 Little does she know she&#039;s about to stumble on 
a mystery even more brain-bending than the last! 
Join Laura on her search for answers through the 
shops of Eurekaberg where cleverly hidden items are
 waiting to be found. Featuring fantastic full-screen 
graphics, an intriguing storyline, and hours of 
seek-and-find fun, Mysteryville 2 is an original 
adventure for the entire family.


Mysteryville

Something very strange is going on in the town of 
Mysteryville and, as an ace reporter for Countryside 
Life Magazine, it&#039;s up to you to find the truth. 
It seems the town cats are disappearing under 
suspicious circumstances. Visit the Mysteryville shops, 
question the residents and examine every detail 
in your search for the answers behind this feline mystery. 
Featuring hours of seek and find fun, bizarre characters, 
and incredible graphics, Mysteryville is a surprising 
adventure for your senses.
